{"tid":1063261,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間避雷針-張賢勝","createTime":"2019-03-15T15:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T17:28:00.000Z","uid":238483,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f10fab30709341cde3f1b4ccf478673d89423f3","tid":1063261,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"「頹廢美&rarr;陽光明朗」BEAST出身的張賢勝入伍前後，形象大轉變！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715145.jpg&h=95aff24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友調侃張賢勝是人間避雷針，沒加入BIGBANG，離開了BEAST，完美躲過了這場災難性事件...<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715141.jpg&h=11e5fcb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日因為「韓娛大地震」事件，不少明星都長期登在韓網熱搜中。 今日因為龍俊亨宣佈退出HIGHLIGHT，連帶了Beast、張賢勝等詞也上了熱搜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715143.jpg&h=53c0fbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網友對比了張賢勝在入伍前後的形象轉變，入伍前以頹廢美著稱的張賢勝，標誌性的妝容是煙熏妝。 在去年7月入伍後的近況被公開，戴著鏡框眼鏡，面容朴素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715147.jpg&h=d78af530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715149.jpg&h=c200e702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-03-14/114827-715151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-03-14%2F114827-715151.jpg&h=069ee8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對此網友評論：「在軍隊的樣子看起來舒服多了、臉色看起來亮多了啊、他就應該在軍隊裡過日子，有人樣了」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白粉仔都有人吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf5e38b152d80a7b75a04dc86d3f4dfd4c5754d","tid":1063261,"uid":55179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"你見過佢食白粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n我就無啦 不過係街見過佢吸人血 應該吸血鬼黎<br />\n成日出街要擦勁厚防曬先唔會死<br />\n利申：賢勝腦粉"}]}